{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PARTY GAME CHAOS</h2><br>Job Joust is a <strong>physics-based party game</strong> where you bump and dunk your friends as a wacky employee. Up to 6 players can fight in this <strong>fast-paced local multiplayer</strong> mayhem.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800510/extras/PingPong.gif?t=1724314585\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BECOME THE ULTIMATE EMPLOYEE</h2><br>Choose <strong>equipments</strong> to improve from round to round and make the best comebacks! From the <strong>giant stealthy C.E.O.</strong> to the <strong>levitating exploding Policeman</strong>, you can become your ultimate self! Combine power-ups together for incredible (or stupid) synergies!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800510/extras/BetteEquipmentGif1-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1724314585\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EASY TO PICK</h2><br>Made to be easily <strong>played by anyone</strong>, it is the perfect tool to settle your couple fights or family conflicts. But hardcore players will find a <strong>great depth</strong> in mastering bounce angles, reads and spikes to demolish their friends in the most satisfying ways.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800510/extras/SimpleInputs.gif?t=1724314585\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">USE YOUR ENVIRONMENT</h2><br>Avoid bumpers, push your victims on lasers and use teleporters to your advantage! <strong>Hazard</strong> plays an important role in your success!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800510/extras/LaserHazard.gif?t=1724314585\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Game Changer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2800510/de1ce2c1fa6af828ab7d6364c7d9402af1e50da6.jpg"},{"name":"It's gonna be Legendary!","pa